short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Extract ld+json scripts from the current webpage

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: LD+JSON Extractor is a simple and efficient tool to extract JSON-LD scripts from any webpage. JSON-LD (JavaScript Object Notation for Linked Data) is a format used to encode linked data in JSON format. This extension helps developers and SEO professionals easily extract and view the structured data embedded in web pages.
